            "Proof of concept exploit for a critical RCE vulnerability in enterprise software. Features custom payload generation and evasion techniques.",
        tags: ["Python", "Exploit Dev", "Network Security"],
        stars: 124,
        url: "#",
    },
    {
        title: "AutoRecon-X",
        description:
            "Automated reconnaissance tool for bug bounty hunting. Integrates multiple scanners and outputs a unified report.",
        tags: ["Bash", "Go", "Automation"],
        stars: 89,
        url: "#",
    },
    {
